      "id": "PopularPost177375",
      "post_content": "[Dawnglow Infusion](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dawnglow Infusion) and [Stream of Life](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stream of Life) are both sorceries. If you play either today in hope of gaining life you probably end dead as you will be burned in response. Pre 6th edition you would have had time to gain that life, but not today.  \n  \nThis is an instant and thus can be used in response to the burn. Resolves first and saves you.",
      "posted_by": "tavaritz",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost177375\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\"><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Dawnglow Infusion\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dawnglow Infusion\">Dawnglow Infusion</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Stream of Life\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stream of Life\">Stream of Life</a> are both sorceries. If you play either today in hope of gaining life you probably end dead as you will be burned in response. Pre 6th edition you would have had time to gain that life, but not today.<br/><br/>This is an instant and thus can be used in response to the burn. Resolves first and saves you.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '177375'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy58371\">tavaritz</span>\r\n                                (7/10/2011 11:41:04 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/